title: Suikoden II PAL (PSX)
description:
SUIKODEN II
PSX RPG from Konami, 1999
EU/PAL Version
English

==============================================

I had been looking for a download of this game for way too long so I ended up tracking down a copy in an online auction. This way, noone else will have to =) You can finally put your Suiko1 PAL savefile to use. 

Fixed from the US/NTSC version:
* Loading a previous gamefile no longer jarbles the old names (TcDohl and such)
* Annallee actually sings in this one
* Several music bugs fixed
* Gibberish-spewing NPC's make sense again. 
This is all according to user reports. Typos are still plentiful though. 

This is my first torrent ever uploaded, so here's hoping it turns out well. The imagefile has been tested for the first 10 minutes on ePSXe, so there shouldn't be any problems.



PS! You can ONLY use the "Load previous gamefile" feature with a save from the PAL-version of Suikoden 1.
